ext_ar":"رَافِضَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, K:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaDN","text_ar":"رَفَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arofaADN","text_ar":"اَرْفَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufuwDN","text_ar":"رُفُوضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to be a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafoDN","text_ar":"رَفْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A herd of gazelles in a state of separation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifaADN","text_ar":"رِفَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEaAmN rafaDN","text_ar":"نَعَامٌ رَفَضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ostriches in separate flocks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Als~afari","text_ar":"فِى السَّفَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsu A^arofaADN","text_ar":"النَّاسُ اَرْفَاضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The men are in a state of separation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersion, in journeying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufuwDu","text_ar":"رُفُوضُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The different parties of men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino kalaA^K","text_ar":"مِنْ كَلَاٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufuwDN","text_ar":"رُفُوضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Scattered pieces of herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jm, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distant one from another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jm, S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufuwDu","text_ar":"رُفُوضُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land which is deserted after having been prohibited to the public:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which has no possessor:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L, K:) so says IDrd; but he adds, or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deserted land"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two cultivated pieces of land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two pieces of land belonging to two tribes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaDN","text_ar":"رَفَضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is large, and in a state of separation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arofaADN","text_ar":"اَرْفَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafoDN","text_ar":"رَفْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAnibN","text_ar":"جَانِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of a thing. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafoDN","text_ar":"رَفْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, ISk, Az, Z,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaDN","text_ar":"رَفَضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, Fr, A'Obeyd, S,) the latter said, in a marginal note in the S, to be the correct form heard from the Arabs, (TA,) or both, (Sgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water; (S, A, K;) and of milk; (A, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remaining in the bottom of a skin or of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juroEap","text_ar":"جُرْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little less than is sufficient to fill a skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arofaADN","text_ar":"اَرْفَاضٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lh.) ―         -b4-  And hence, the former, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food that is sufficient to sustain life;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quwtN","text_ar":"قُوتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","S","K","Jm","O","L","TA","IAar","ISk","Az","Z","Sgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}